property_address: ['Room in Culver City, California, United States']
listing_description: ["I have a room available in a large custom built three story 8 bedroom Mediterranean style house. I live in the house with other tenants. I like to have the option to have a spare room for friends or AIRBNB guests. The house is in a very safe neighborhood on a cul de sac. Sony studios is a few blocks away as well as restaurant row in downtown Culver City.This is not a party house and everyone is respectful to each other. Please respect the privacy of the long term tenants.The spaceMy  house  is  custom built three story Mediterranean style house. Wi-fi available throughout house.  I have two dogs, an adorable Cavalier King Charles spaniel and rescue dog.  Unfortunately I can't have other guest pets.  Plenty of street parking.   Very safe neighborhood and  property is located on a cul de sac.Guest accessAIRBNB guest access to the house involves going through a driveway gate that is to the left of a red brick building at the front of the property. The entrance to the three story Mediterranean house is down the driveway. The front door is never locked . Open it and your room with the name on the door B1 will be on your immediate right.Common areas include bathrooms on the first and second floor.The kitchen area and 3rd floor are for tenant use only!During your stayNo Airbnb guests allowed in kitchen or on third floor. That area is reserved for long term tenants only. Please respect privacy of long term tenants.Me your host will be able to help with suggestions on what to see and where to go if you wish.Other things to noteThis is not a party house!No smoking on premises. Smoking is only allowed outside the house, off the property. No candles or fire in house."]
